{"tid":2345682,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"上司無時無刻都搵我，應該點應對","createTime":"2020-12-29T16:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T17:44:48.000Z","uid":357927,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d608be82dd4515af9ad0d7a1faa80119047dfa2f","tid":2345682,"uid":357927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:48:21.000Z","msg":"讀完書第一份工，7月頭開始。做緊啲進口日本嘢但香港人開嘅港企。7日AL冇醫保 as expected(剝削是基本吧)。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來好地地正常返工放工，依家返工真係煩L到唔想做。學唔到嘢唔講，返觀塘好L遠，返工煉獄唔係浪得虛名架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。最PK我個上司任何時間都會whatsapp問我搞呢樣問個樣，仲要成日打電話嚟。(我係返寫字樓工 Monday to Friday，9點到6點) 大佬試過weekend同人食緊飯都打嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。初初都有聽，後尾操底就成日唔聽，條on9仔都get到唔會係啲應該係我嘅時間搵我。<br />\n但近期又故態復萌，又成日辦公時間外搵我搞公司嘢。<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位巴絲你哋有咩辦法唔俾返工啲嘢滲入咗自己私人時間/生活。PK好L後悔比咗自己個personal number條PK<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />why is life so hard <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aecda63f444b8e38a728e6e05480a506df04b263","tid":2345682,"uid":99461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:53:02.000Z","msg":"Gay"},{"pid":"70054d3811a09691bbb13c9f4c60e5d3553c095c","tid":2345682,"uid":383970,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:54:24.000Z","msg":"講尼d, 我上司今日要我add佢facebook, 我將2年嘅facebook post自我審查左一次後 被逼add左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6db90909d7ecef1a476e663d64cf9b1ee7ab7ca","tid":2345682,"uid":343544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"下畫先開始應機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537e023c2e4fa99d9bfd5d54c869db9eeb0003b5","tid":2345682,"uid":3185,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:57:06.000Z",